properties.Name: TransunionInquiry
properties.Description:
Displays which companies viewed the consumer's credit file.

Includes date the inquiry occurred, and the inquiring subscriber's TransUnion-assigned member number and name.

Columns.Name: TransunionInquiryNumber
Columns.Description: The TransUnion Inquiry Number uniquely identifies an inquiry within a TransUnion Credit Report.
